rComments: As a female, i found this material very interesting. She knows what she's talking about (this is in fact what she researchers after all) but it can be a little confusing.. that being said if you ask a lot of questions and attend class regularly it isn't too tough. The hard part about tests is the open ended and fill in blanks. Go to this class!!
